==製作==
拍攝預計於2015年4月會在[[紐約市|紐約市]]和[[水牛城|水牛城]]進行，估算會在當地花了7000萬美元的拍攝費用<ref>{{cite news|last1=FERMINO|first1=JENNIFER|title='Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 2' to film in New York City and Buffalo, bringing an estimated $70 million in spending|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2-film-nyc-buffalo-article-1.2157366|accessdate=2015-03-21|publisher=nydailynews.com|date=2015-03-20|archive-date=2015-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150321080550/http://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2-film-nyc-buffalo-article-1.2157366|dead-url=no}}</ref>。正式拍攝於2015年4月27日在紐約市進行的同時，還被發現劇組在[[曼哈頓中城|曼哈頓中城]]取景<ref>{{cite news|title=First look at 'Teenage Mutant Ninja 2′ filming in NYC!|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2015/04/29/first-look-at-teenage-mutant-ninja-2-filming-in-nyc/|accessdate=2015-04-29|work=onlocationvacations.com|date=2015-04-29|archive-date=2020-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920085851/https://onlocationvacations.com/2015/04/29/first-look-at-teenage-mutant-ninja-2-filming-in-nyc/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在水牛城的拍攝於2015年5月4日開始，並包含[[肯辛頓高速公路|肯辛頓高速公路]]（紐約州33號公路）<ref>{{cite news|last1=Gryta|first1=Matt|title='Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 2' crew thanks city for "incredible experience"|url=http://www.buffalonews.com/city-region/buffalo/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2-crew-thanks-city-for-incredible-experience-20150416|accessdate=2015-04-17|work=buffalonews.com|date=2015-04-17|archive-date=2016-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160104114046/http://www.buffalonews.com/city-region/buffalo/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2-crew-thanks-city-for-incredible-experience-20150416|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Cowabunga! "Ninja Turtles" action starts Monday on the Kensington  - The Buffalo News|url = http://www.buffalonews.com/city-region/cowabunga-ninja-turtles-action-starts-monday-on-the-kensington-20150502|accessdate = 2015-05-02|archive-date = 2016-03-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303174122/http://www.buffalonews.com/city-region/cowabunga-ninja-turtles-action-starts-monday-on-the-kensington-20150502|dead-url = no}}</ref>，於2015年5月17日結束<ref>{{cite news|last1=Belcher|first1=Mark|title=Buffalo to be taken over by Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles for two weeks|url=http://wivb.com/2015/04/15/buffalo-opens-up-for-teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2-but-shuts-down-some-roads/|accessdate=2015-04-17|work=wivb.com|date=2015-04-15|archive-date=2016-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160220163258/http://wivb.com/2015/04/15/buffalo-opens-up-for-teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2-but-shuts-down-some-roads/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。拍攝於2015年8月宣布結束，接著開始進入後期製作階段<ref>{{cite news|last1=Cruz|first1=Alex|title='Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 2' Currently In The Works; 'Half Shell' Updates You Might Have Missed|url=http://www.jobsnhire.com/articles/23647/20150803/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2-films-half-shell-updates-you-might-have-missed.htm|accessdate=2015-08-11|work=jobsnhire.com|date=2015-08-03|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929092633/https://www.jobsnhire.com/articles/23647/20150803/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2-films-half-shell-updates-you-might-have-missed.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=The Street Transcripts|title=Viacom (VIA) Earnings Report: Q3 2015 Conference Call Transcript|url=http://www.thestreet.com/story/13247406/6/viacom-via-earnings-report-q3-2015-conference-call-transcript.html|accessdate=2015-08-11|work=The Street|date=2015-08-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151022121736/http://www.thestreet.com/story/13247406/6/viacom-via-earnings-report-q3-2015-conference-call-transcript.html|archivedate=2015年10月22日}}</ref>。

==發行==
本片於2016年5月22日在[[紐約市|紐約市]]首映，2016年6月3日在美國各地正式上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gofobo.com/index.php/main/movie_landing/WUV4QWY4NDQxNA%3D%3D|title=TEENAGE MUTANT NINJA TURTLES: OUT OF THE SHADOWS - Landing Page|publisher=|access-date=2016-06-01|archive-date=2020-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916054208/https://gofobo.com/index.php/main/movie_landing/WUV4QWY4NDQxNA%3D%3D|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而英國則於2016年5月30日上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.paramount.co.uk/movies/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-out-shadows|title=Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Out of the Shadows - Official UK Site  - Paramount Pictures UK|publisher=|access-date=2016-03-10|archive-date=2020-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920063944/https://www.paramount.co.uk/movies/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-out-shadows|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===評價===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度37%，基於169條評論，平均分為4.69/10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/teenage_mutant_ninja_turtles_out_of_the_shadows/ |title=Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Out of the Shadows (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2016-05-31 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116052234/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/teenage_mutant_ninja_turtles_out_of_the_shadows |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得到40分，[[IMDB|IMDB]]上得6分，評價兩極<ref name="Meta">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2 |title=Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Out of the Shadows (2016) |website=Metacritic |accessdate=2016-06-02 |archive-date=2016-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603194924/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。整體評價比前集好上一些。

===票房===
在[[美國|美國]]和[[加拿大|加拿大]]，專家預測從4000間戲院能獲得3000萬至4000萬美元左右的票房，部分[[分析師|分析師]]認為甚至可能會更高<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4191&p=.htm|title='X-Men' & 'Alice' Lead Soft Memorial Day Weekend; Disney Tops $4 Billion Worldwide|author=Brad Brevet|work=''[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]''|date=2016-05-29|accessdate=2016-05-29|archive-date=2016-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160529232748/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=4191&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="preview">{{cite web|url=https://www.thewrap.com/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-sequel-to-top-box-office-but-faces-troubled-waters-ahead/|title=‘Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles’ Sequel to Top Box Office, But Faces Troubled Waters Ahead|author=Meriah Doty|work=''[[The_Wrap|The Wrap]]''|date=2016-05-31|accessdate=2016-06-01|archive-date=2016-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602170137/http://www.thewrap.com/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-sequel-to-top-box-office-but-faces-troubled-waters-ahead/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/06/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-out-of-the-shadows-me-before-you-pop-star-box-office-preview-1201765435/|title=‘Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles’ Bound To Toss ‘X-Men’ Out Of First Place – Weekend B.O. Preview|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline|Deadline]]''|date=2016-06-01|accessdate=2016-06-02|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108090240/https://deadline.com/2016/06/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-out-of-the-shadows-me-before-you-pop-star-box-office-preview-1201765435/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。結果也符合大多數分析師預期，美國首映週末票房為3530萬美元，位居當週冠軍，但和前集的6560萬美元（不含北美外票房）相比則下跌了45%<ref name="Scott">{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/06/05/weekend-box-office-ninja-turtles-2-stumbles-me-before-you-shines-popstar-bombs/#6a624b1d5905|title=Weekend Box Office: 'Ninja Turtles 2' Stumbles, 'Me Before You' Shines, 'Popstar' Bombs|author=Scott Mendelson|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|date=2016-06-05|accessdate=2016-06-05|archive-date=2020-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920100630/https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2016/06/05/weekend-box-office-ninja-turtles-2-stumbles-me-before-you-shines-popstar-bombs/#6a624b1d5905|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在中国大陆，首周3天收获2.1亿人民币，列當周末第一位，最終票房累计3.92亿人民币<ref>[http://piaofang.maoyan.com/movie/13511 《忍者神龟2：破影而出》電影介紹] {{Wayback|url=http://piaofang.maoyan.com/movie/13511 |date=20200916035456 }} 貓眼票房</ref>，略高於前集的3.87亿人民币<ref>[http://piaofang.maoyan.com/movie/245931 《忍者神龟：变种时代》電影介紹] {{Wayback|url=http://piaofang.maoyan.com/movie/245931 |date=20200916042043 }} 貓眼票房</ref>。

